{"tid":2036871,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日我會出，頭先我喺我隻貓耳邊講咗句：我愛你","createTime":"2020-05-26T17:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T19:56:20.000Z","uid":227212,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d462a1a45d4f86ad943317336ce32a3881eafb50","tid":2036871,"uid":227212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:05:21.000Z","msg":"呢幾日陪住屋企隻貓 <br />\n摸摸佢頭頂d毛<br />\n佢個頭係咁貼住我隻手擰<br />\n佢'hi'夠就擰咩面 望窗<br />\n佢望風景 我望佢<br />\n好想世界停喺嗰一刻<br />\n<br />\n我強行攬咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺佢耳邊講咗句<br />\n我愛你呀死港女<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知聽日會係咩情況 我會睇情況行動<br />\n最後一晚嘅感覺久違啦 我又開始淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋可唔可以對我講句：<br />\n手足無事嘅 唔驚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">ps 又要好神經質咁數要帶嘅野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"d45edd147c98ff9654f341d1115b269301c25446","tid":2036871,"uid":139294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:06:45.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好驚見唔番隻肥野<br />\n但我仲驚將來"},{"pid":"c64dc64b43d8485ea987e5907eb6b48c3306965e","tid":2036871,"uid":56394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:07:44.000Z","msg":"唔應該當今晚係最後一晚<br />\n長路漫漫<br />\n保重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae62863593e0b10eccb7401052d67681215cb9e5","tid":2036871,"uid":60539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:08:15.000Z","msg":"我隻貓同我講 聽日醒定啲就無事喎"},{"pid":"0fb7f64420367be85298f53ecf78be41724c496e","tid":2036871,"uid":300243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"手足聽日真係一定要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" c